{"tid":2077225,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"直幡掛獅山 籲上街抗惡法","createTime":"2020-06-24T06:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T07:46:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7bed075474e3f7554e661ee7984138745e7ffc31","tid":2077225,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:29:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200624/K4WXPUN5TQDEMSMEJM5N53MRQY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2FK4WXPUN5TQDEMSMEJM5N53MRQY%2F&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPnIsb0SIwbGp5IKHDv9YBGc%3D&h=6be1d18d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2FK4WXPUN5TQDEMSMEJM5N53MRQY%2F&h=1d8fbe48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200624/K4WXPUN5TQDEMSMEJM5N53MRQY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n直幡掛獅山 籲上街抗惡法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KIKC7F66LFVBTRDAIHW53AWYRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKIKC7F66LFVBTRDAIHW53AWYRQ.jpg&h=a2c02f8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昨早獅子山掛有巨型直幡，寫上「七一上街抗惡法」。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】獅子山、筆架山等山頭不時掛出大型直幡表達政治訴求。有途人昨早發現獅子山掛有一幅長約3米乘30米、寫上「七一上街抗惡法」巨型直幡，消防接報到場再發現另一幅直幡，一併拆除帶走，料有巿民不滿中央強推港版國安法，鼓勵更多人上街抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年至少11次<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：刑事案法官絕非特首指派<br />\n<br />\n昨早7時許，有途人報案稱面向黃大仙的獅子山近獅子頭位置，有人懸掛一幅長約3米乘30米的直幡，直幡上黑底白字寫上「七一上街抗惡法」，消防及政府飛行服務隊人員到場移除，同時發現附近一幅2米乘1米的直幡，一併帶走，交由漁護署部門跟進。<br />\n<br />\n自去年反修例運動爆發，。。。。嘲諷6.12一周年紀念活動中，有防暴警員向外籍記者呼喊「I can't breathe（我無法呼吸）」。。。。，事後該名防暴警被上級訓示注意個人言行。"},{"pid":"6b981363bf10cba5cf78cb12539e709e2d550cb3","tid":2077225,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:43:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d14efcbea1f3c081b5d5f5bf88b86af19a84747","tid":2077225,"uid":110079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:46:53.000Z","msg":"628靜默遊行 71大遊行<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iVkuPiA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiVkuPiA.jpg&h=a40c696e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KKJsAYA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKKJsAYA.jpg&h=f651646f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}